'''Lunis At Mengellat''', d amedyaz, d acennay i gellan yiwen seg inaẓuren imeẓẓwa ugar (plus populaires) n izwawen. Ilul ass n 17 Yennayer 1950, deg taddart n Iɣil Bbwamas ufella n [[Tamurt n leqbayel|tmurt n Leqbayel]] ar tama n Micli. Isɛa sdis warrac garasen yiwen d anazur n ccna : [[Ğeɛfer At Mengellat]].

== Temẓi ines ==

D annegaru ger sdis (6) wayetma-s - 3 n tullas d sin warrac - isɛada temẓi ines qesiḥet di taddart-is and yeɣra yiwen usegwas send ad serɣen irumyen aɣerbaz anda yella yeqqar. Tawacult-is llan di imzenza di [[Wehran]] anda sɛan tiḥuna.  Mi ikfa trad mgal Franṣa deg 1962, Lunis At Mengellat iruḥ ar [[Lezzayer tamanaɣt]] akw d watmaten-is Smaɛil d Aḥmed. Din ikcem ar uɣerbaz wis amezwaru (primaire) di 'Chmaps de Manœuvres'. Din iɣra tizrawt uwizi (Études collégiales) azal n 3 isegwasen, s wanda id yefeɣ s usileɣ (formation) n wayen umi neqqar s tefranṣiṣt ''Ébéniste''. Deg segwas anegaru Lunis At Mengellat iğa leqray-as imi imut gma-s amuqwran di yiwet n Laksida n tkarust, d netta ilan iɛgcit seg asmi iruḥen imawlan-is ar Wehran.

Asmi yeqqar, ila iḥemel tasekla, d yiwen uselmad d amusegmi (pédagogue) id a t-tiḥemlen. Dɣa yuɣal ixedem weḥdes isefra. I waken ad yečč aɣrum-is, ila yxedem di yiwet n tneɣlaft di lezzayer, send ad idfer abrid n ccna.

== Amecwar-is di ccna ==

Ibda i tikkelt tamezwarut ccna deg 1967. Ur iɛṭel ara iğat lukan mačči d imedukal i s dizzin i waken ad as bedlen tikti. D Wahab i gellan si twacult-is i tibwin ar yiwet n tedwilt, iɣennayen uzekka, n umaṭaf wis II n Rradyu n [[Lezzayer]], i g selḥay unazur n ccna [[Crif Xeddam]]. Icna-d taɣuct-is tamezwarut '''Ma trud ula d nek Kter''' i g-xdem asmi isɛa 16 isegwasen. 

Deg 1968, netta d kra imedukwal, xedmen yiwet n tarbaɛt umi seman Imaziɣen. Llan accenun di tmeɣriwin yakw di tmurt n leqbayel, ladɣa di tasaft. Deg 1970, tarbaɛt aki tuɣal texsi, Lunis At Mengellat yuɣal-ed ar taddart-is Iɣil Bbwamas, yezweğ, i xedem  d amaray di 'Kasma' n temnaṭ ines. Kra n waguren kan, iruḥ s ddaw isenğaq, ar laasker di [[Blida]] isɛeda 6 waguren, ma di [[Qsenṭina]], 18 waguren.

== Asekles n tezlatin-is timezwura ==

I tikelt tamezwarut d Wahab, i sittilin, i tiɛawnen ad isekles kuz (4) n tezlatin deg segwas 1969, garasent tizlit ''Ma trud ula d nek kter''. Anecta ilad ar umazrag Yaḥya Lhadi, di Wehran, illan d yiwet n tmusni n Wahab. Asmi illa di laasker, anazur n ccna [[Kamal Ḥemmadi]] i gellan d ameddakel-is, i xedma-s tanalt (contact) d kra imazragen. Ma d ittruḥu s turagt (permission) di tagara umalas, Kamal Ḥamadi i ttağas yiwen u 'Studio' n unazur amuqwran [[Maḥbub Bati]] i waken ad isekles. Send ad yeṭef tamacint ar Qsinṭina i waken ad yuɣal ar laasker, i ttağa-yas tasfift i Kamal Ḥemmadi i waken ad iqeleb af imazragen.   

Dɣa yiwen deg imazragen i weṣat i waken ad yawed taɣuct n Awḥid Yusef: ''Ih a Muhand a Madam Servi Latay''. Lamaana amedyaz Lunis At Mengellat, g-imiren ittwali ar lembɛiad. D ayen yellan, imi simi bdan kan isegwasen n 1970, yuɣal Lunis At Mengellat yettwasen mebla ma yezra, ladɣa s tuɣac 'A Lwiza', 'Ma selbeɣ' i g-sekles netta yella di laasker.

== Isegwasen n ureɣ ==

Seg segwasen akin, yuɣal Lunis At Mengellat d azamul muqren i yal azwaw, ladɣa wid i ḥemlen ccna n Tayri, n dunit, d tsartit. Seg segwasen n 1980, yabda aḥric wayeḍ deg mecwar-is n ccna, imi iffeɣ si tuɣac n tayri ar t-id n tanegmit n tamagit (la revendication identitaire), anecta ibaned ugar si tamrawt (décennie) ar zdat.  


Iɛedda i tikkelt tamezwarut di tazeqa 'Olympia' di 'Paris' deg usegwas n 1978. Isyin anda iɛeda, ama di tazeqa n 'Zénith' di 'Paris' deg 1985, ama di Lezzayer tamanaɣt, [[Tizi Wezzu]], [[Bgayet]], atg, iččur d imeshaniyen.  Anazur Lunis At Mengelat icna aṭas isegwasen s yiwen n alal kan: tagiṭart neɣ a mundul. Armi kradeṭ (30) isegwasen seld, ibda i sekcam alalen nniden, ladɣa tajewaqt akw d klabyi.

Ar unemzel (unanimité) n waṭas n tsuta n wid i ḥemlen Lunis At Mengellat, ila d win iqedcen ameslay aken ur llan aṭas am netta. I sexdam awal, ittak-as anamek d w-azal, iqqar-d ayen illan, d wayen ur nelli, d ayen ara yelin. Segmi Lunis At Mengellat qarren-as medden d amusnaw, daɣen d amesnagay iwen (philosophe unique) ar izwawen. Lunis At Mengellet isekles ugar n 200 n tezlatin.

